repairmen disappeared.
   Shoppers could hear their newly elected deputies criticizing
Politburo members and demanding control over the dreaded KBG
everywhere.
   As they moved out of earshot of the broadcast at a checkout
stand, they could walk outside to hear the words emanating from a
car radio.
